<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Pissa House - Mini Pizzas</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #fff8f0;
      color: #333;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header {
      background-color: #e63946;
      color: white;
      padding: 30px 0;
    }

    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 3em;
    }

    header p {
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      font-size: 1.2em;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    .content img {
      width: 300px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 15px 25px;
      background-color: #ffbe0b;
      color: #000;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }

    .button:hover {
      background-color: #f77f00;
    }

    footer {
      background-color: #e63946;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px 0;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Pissa House</h1>
    <p>As melhores mini pizzas da cidade!</p>
  </header>

  <div class="content">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1601924582975-7b7bfbf6b9d3" alt="Mini pizza deliciosa">
    <h2>Mini no tamanho, gigante no sabor!</h2>
    <p>Entrega rápida, ingredientes frescos e muito amor em cada pedacinho. Faça seu pedido agora!</p>
    <a href="https://wa.me/SEUNUMEROAQUI" class="button">Pedir pelo WhatsApp</a>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 Pissa House. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
